Jo Ann Sayers https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo_Ann_Sayers 0 Jo Ann Sayers (born Miriam Lucille Lilygren, October 22, 1918 – November 14, 2011) was an American actress who was active in Broadway and in Hollywood films. Her film career spanned the 1930s through the 1950s.
